    "Despite providing insights into the impact of these initiatives on student outcomes and teaching quality, subjective data were not thoroughly examined.",
    "Future studies should explore Chinese teachers' challenges in integrating STEM into their classrooms.",
    "The need for standardized evaluation methods in TPD programs is unclear, particularly for assessing the effectiveness of STEM instruction.",
    "Sharing these best practices across regions holds great potential, suggesting a future where collaborative and effective educational experiences become standard.",
    "Furthermore, as the global educational landscape shifts towards STEAM, future research and TPD programs should consider this broader framework to enhance the effectiveness of teacher training further and ultimately improve student outcomes in both STEM and STEAM disciplines."
